# Dev.to Article – Day 02

## Title:  
BubuVerse: StarlightCoin (STC) Tokenomics Explained

## Summary:  
This Dev.to article explains how StarlightCoin (STC) works within the BubuVerse economy.  
It covers the tokenomics design that aligns in-game progression with real value through:  
- Starlight Energy → STC conversion  
- Long-term token distribution  
- Player rewards and sustainable participation

